data.description: Welcome Home! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is located in a fantastic neighborhood and sits on just over an acre of land. Step inside and you will be greeted by beautiful updates and trendy colors that create a warm and inviting atmosphere. The living room, kitchen, dining room, hallways, and laundry room have all been freshly painted. The home features upgrades such as gutters, a sunroom with windows, an extended deck with stairs, and a 10x12 detached storage shed. If you love to cook, the kitchen is a must-see with granite countertops and modern stainless-steel appliances. The roof is original from 2016, and while the water heater is original to the home, the excess water tank was replaced just 3 months ago. The HVAC system was replaced early in 2022, and the septic tank was pumped in the same year. There is no gas service in the home, but the fireplace utilizes a propane gas cylinder tank located at the back of the home. Step outside to the screened-in porch, perfect for relaxing and entertaining. The large windows fill the home with natural sunlight, creating a cheerful and bright living space. Plus, the fully fenced backyard ensures privacy and security for your family. For added assurance, the property features a security system, including a ring doorbell. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this property your new home!
